Chrome Extension for Data Analysis
  • javacript
  • googleapi
  • typescript
Apr 30, 2019

This is chrome web extension that is designed to analyze any object that will be triggered by double click. The data triggered from that will be sent to a google sheet that has to be configured before make this extension working as the google doesn’t allow to create files through script due to security reason.
